{
  "stem": "26486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were going to enter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they-- if we wanted or not, they were going to enter France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when, I told you, that we decided not to stay in-- in the north of France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to Paris because my parents were afraid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, my daughter was just a little young girl, 12 years old, and I was still young.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my parents didn't want us to be there, exposed, at the hands of the Germans if they came in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Paris where my sister, oldest sister, was living with her husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was director, at that time, of the Guaranty Trust Company, the bank in New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they found us a place to live in Paris, and we stayed in Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we stayed there all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even when I was arrested, my parents still had the same apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So Yvonne had been living in Paris before you arrived?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I must tell you, I wasn't very fond of, of-- that's a culture that I, I didn't care for too much.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're very harsh people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're hard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're not that friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now maybe, but at that time they were not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, I didn't care so much for Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I loved Switzerland, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Italy I liked very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany,?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know they, they were mean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even after the war they didn't like us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't say all the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're, you know-- I've met some nice German people too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I mean the Nazi crowd, they were terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they still are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They will never change.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Paris?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
